99
00:07:58,020 --> 00:08:03,020
 And yet love never ends.

100
00:08:03,020 --> 00:08:05,020
 And it begins right now.

101
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:09,020
 So many of us do not feel like love has actually begun.

102
